title: Ep - 81 - JENNY MCCARTHY
description:
Actress, author, and host Jenny McCarthy reveals the worst part of filming Jenny Loves Donnie, her assessment of Hugh Hefner and his girlfriends on The Girls Next Door, why she is obsessed with 90 Day Fiancé, and the reason she is losing interest in the Real Housewives. 


Ben Mandelker from Watch What Crappens reviews an episode of Hotel Impossible. 


Josh Murray from Party Down South reviews the premiere episode of Real Housewives of Beverly Hills.
